imdb.plot outline: #CAKE is a hour-long serial narrative comedy about a manhunt for a high priced assassin who murders for digital currency (Bitcoin) , the detectives who track him, and a enthused entrepreneur who runs a bitcoin mining operation. In a perfect world do you want money or power? You want the power to create your own money.
